{"tid":758521,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"10大最乞人憎 T V B 藝人 🙄","createTime":"2018-07-27T18:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T18:44:11.000Z","uid":44730,"like":12,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f2e807f5a3e17dd0edce482addbddb7d72dd7f","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"<strong>網民票選「10大最乞人憎TVB藝人」</strong><br />\n<br />\n每個人都會有唔同口味，有時鍾意同討厭嘅嘢都唔一樣。最近有網民搞咗個「我厭惡的十大無綫男女藝人」投票， 大家心入面都有人選吧？睇吓佢哋入唔入圍！<br />\n<br />\n撰文：對白Cap圖王、Cherry@Central｜圖片來源：藝人IG，劇照<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第10位&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n王浩信愈來愈紅，憑《不懂撒嬌的女人》「Saving」成新一代暖男。但近幾年佢嘅緋聞冇停過，黃心穎、蔡思貝、江嘉敏都係緋聞女友。依排仲有傳同靚老婆陳自瑤離婚，令佢嘅形象嚴重插水！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/vincentwong07_30906258_184614138927750_1953560587480858624_n_8362277835b1a5efa5158a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fvincentwong07_30906258_184614138927750_1953560587480858624_n_8362277835b1a5efa5158a.jpg&h=50f76086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/vincentwong07_22344611_1689145481137005_2456894440623570944_n_5551665435b1a5ef864bec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fvincentwong07_22344611_1689145481137005_2456894440623570944_n_5551665435b1a5ef864bec.jpg&h=3a967b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/bb_6025754545b191bf875019_8167884775b1a5f0167689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fbb_6025754545b191bf875019_8167884775b1a5f0167689.jpg&h=a868006b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"338330aeb82c55aad8d2720520d7107cf98925a9","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":10,"dislike":60,"score":-50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:38:47.000Z","msg":"第9位&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n出自巨聲幫嘅林師傑之前就經常見報，因為佢有過唔少緋聞女友。連舊愛鄧穎芝都暗寸佢多囡囡，所以網民對佢嘅觀感都麻麻哋！<br />\n<br />\n和舊愛鄧穎芝拍拖期間，有傳女方曾當場目擊林師傑同𡃁模Gwen在車內「激戰」，女方即時喊住走人！而林師傑隨後亦有上傳IG同微博借劇集角色名自嘲：「上官飛，你今天又得罪了誰被打了&hellip;」！<br />\n<br />\n而最近向拍拖3年的女友歐陽巧瑩求婚成功，今年年尾11月正式註冊，唔知成為人夫後大家對佢又會唔會多番啲好感呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/21271261_1542704925752584_544544096392431292_n_10658012195b1a66caa5df6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F21271261_1542704925752584_544544096392431292_n_10658012195b1a66caa5df6.jpg&h=0d4fd69b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/23244026_1597867380236338_1432533126841377267_n_11733821275b1a66cb8f659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F23244026_1597867380236338_1432533126841377267_n_11733821275b1a66cb8f659.jpg&h=688fa93e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/-2018-07-26-8.18.10_5898902655b59bcc116996.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F-2018-07-26-8.18.10_5898902655b59bcc116996.jpg&h=19f6509e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81a0d0aa409a82d1b72a9fdcf0982b9cba362495","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":7,"dislike":44,"score":-37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:39:10.000Z","msg":"第8位&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n崔建邦歷年傳過多次緋聞，上年與林珊珊細女李怡(野人)分手後，最近被傳與52歲的陳雅倫「撻著」。不過最令觀眾討厭的是當年被踏爆打女朋友，網民都成日話佢係賤男，所以多負評係正常嘅。<br />\n<br />\n而最近崔建邦伯樂陳志雲個演嘢《志雲尋志雲》會晚晚重提住佢打女人一事！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/amigochoi_26226816_2088345314728644_6865771557872992256_n_16838961085b1a67a100385.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Famigochoi_26226816_2088345314728644_6865771557872992256_n_16838961085b1a67a100385.jpg&h=5b9d4f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/-2018-04-06-8.58.17_20309122105ac76efc3e2f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F-2018-04-06-8.58.17_20309122105ac76efc3e2f6.jpg&h=5cddf736&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad0b76e1da0f342cc7cc7ee2d7fdfb36e62a6efd","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":9,"dislike":57,"score":-48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"第7位&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n黃翠如榜上有名會令大家嚇一跳，到底翠點解有份？！不過有網民話，因為大台谷佢谷得太勁，差唔多套套劇集都見到佢，演技麻麻嘅佢永遠都係一號表情，真係睇到唔想睇！<br />\n<br />\n在2012年投身TVB後，同年7月開始拍攝劇集，透過《師父&middot;明白了》擔正做第一女主角，隨後在《愛我請留言》中再度擔正第一女主角，並獲得「飛躍進步女藝員」獎項，不過網民就對呢個結果唔係幾受落啦<br />\n<br />\n亦有網民指翠如拍《使徒行者2》僅用咗一個表情拍完成套戲，其實大家都唔係咁討厭嘅，如果佢演技再好多啲就perfect啦⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201709/20170927130748_0_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201709%2F20170927130748_0_1.jpg&h=db149b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/zvcuftn613sngplwl5q-8wqsofimacvimell4phcw_128200525b5aca21c6e9c-1050x700.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fzvcuftn613sngplwl5q-8wqsofimacvimell4phcw_128200525b5aca21c6e9c-1050x700.jpeg&h=6fac6581&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a3d175e69ea35aaaafd3defc6f1b6056930fac7","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":11,"dislike":223,"score":-212,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:40:00.000Z","msg":"第6位 <br />\n<br />\n坤哥俾網民嘅形象係傻吓傻吓，但後來佢被傳背住前緋聞女友Super girl成員Aka識女仔，感情生活好亂。依家好多人都話佢係「扮傻扮被動」「偽毒」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/1_17899534715a2919b6becc7_14265304225b1a69b710852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F1_17899534715a2919b6becc7_14265304225b1a69b710852.jpg&h=1db688bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/151f16a8e35a1a23adfd032e4fa1b5b3_804293605ad86a0251d90_15514816145b1a69b8e3505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F151f16a8e35a1a23adfd032e4fa1b5b3_804293605ad86a0251d90_15514816145b1a69b8e3505.jpg&h=b051dc6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/-2018-07-27-3.42.11_4560503875b5acce9ac0ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F-2018-07-27-3.42.11_4560503875b5acce9ac0ee.jpg&h=47dd7fc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85210f05a2c64d2a0e5efa71c1c1480140c586c4","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":88,"score":-84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:40:25.000Z","msg":"第5位 <br />\n<br />\n出身自巨聲幫嘅何雁詩喺上年被指，介入鄭俊弘同未婚妻，做小三！之後鄭俊弘與何雁詩突然十指緊扣現身機場，高調承認戀情，令到好多網民都反晒白眼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/stephanieeho_34372359_1864546727179511_5707630521245237248_n_17374273765b1a6b53b9099.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fstephanieeho_34372359_1864546727179511_5707630521245237248_n_17374273765b1a6b53b9099.jpg&h=3aeb3bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/-2018-07-27-3.46.31_2735769405b5acdeab717d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F-2018-07-27-3.46.31_2735769405b5acdeab717d.jpg&h=f4931e7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7dceb09ae0a53ae0346eddb395cb0dae563190c","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":9,"dislike":204,"score":-195,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:40:48.000Z","msg":"第4位 <br />\n<br />\n叻哥經常公開講自己嘅睇法，獲獲都語出驚人。佢寸寸貢嘅口氣都令唔少網民覺得反感！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/f806-fykywuc4823268-1_7173915425b1a6cb10063f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Ff806-fykywuc4823268-1_7173915425b1a6cb10063f.jpg&h=8d2422b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/021228_73514d903cec4cc6e3f100b242ef1450.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F021228_73514d903cec4cc6e3f100b242ef1450.gif&h=ccad7e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/lRK37Ff2Gyk/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FlRK37Ff2Gyk%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=7176da96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d04397c5c886521289366f743b2627334c2ca97","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":12,"dislike":119,"score":-107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:41:13.000Z","msg":"第3位 <br />\n<br />\n溝女王嘅李思捷緋聞好多，但佢都仲好有性格咁話：「係人都溝女，唔溝女才是乖仔？我覺得很荒謬，俾女溝又被人罵，溝女又被人罵，不如孤單一個就最乖？我覺得好無聊。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/5a7de2d8940250e01e8e1cb2ea49ddf9_3059972465b1a6da10045c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F5a7de2d8940250e01e8e1cb2ea49ddf9_3059972465b1a6da10045c.jpg&h=050199ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/-2018-07-27-3.56.02_4525469215b5ad03dc4ff1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F-2018-07-27-3.56.02_4525469215b5ad03dc4ff1.jpg&h=dfe03303&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"502f046b7e8b31d9d4e3b2297aeb849060c47df6","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":7,"dislike":230,"score":-223,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:41:36.000Z","msg":"第2位 <br />\n<br />\n阿Bob成日都喺電視見到佢，但佢觀眾緣實在唔OK。新一輯《美女廚房》佢都有份㗎，不過好多人都話佢唔好笑要罷睇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/bob_lamshingbun_33911548_2167111596835343_6562903082772987904_n_16978368345b1a6ecdeecf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fbob_lamshingbun_33911548_2167111596835343_6562903082772987904_n_16978368345b1a6ecdeecf7.jpg&h=2bcdef54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/2018-06-02-9.59.42_15464224585b12ab358c774-800x500_3935073475b1a6ecce80d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F2018-06-02-9.59.42_15464224585b12ab358c774-800x500_3935073475b1a6ecce80d9.jpg&h=79fbfc54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44d85326d3c1c000e135373a579391a618ff63a5","tid":758521,"uid":44730,"like":11,"dislike":169,"score":-158,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:41:53.000Z","msg":"第1位&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n鄭俊弘被爆出搭上何雁詩，封佢為「世紀賤男」。仲有傳佢因為依件事，態度欠佳，令原本佢喺《逆緣》所演角色，最後被陳家樂取代！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.kingofcapture.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/fredcheng83_28434628_1877295918982286_2683812427753062400_n_7652412845b1a6fd75d4f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.kingofcapture.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Ffredcheng83_28434628_1877295918982286_2683812427753062400_n_7652412845b1a6fd75d4f9.jpg&h=082ec386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/-2018-07-27-4.01.52_14286680845b5ad17f7ca8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F-2018-07-27-4.01.52_14286680845b5ad17f7ca8d.jpg&h=7175952a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bb84a7cf14709022f3bd7c898ceb0a3321b7d5f","tid":758521,"uid":179503,"like":1,"dislike":81,"score":-80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T18:45